    <h1>Climbing Kilimanjaro in the Rainy Season: Should You Go?</h1>
    <p>The long rains (April-May) and short rains (November) on Mount Kilimanjaro. What it's actually like, the routes that still work, and whether the rainy season climb is for you.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
